Hotel Bookings Analysis Project
📋 Overview
This project is a complete end‑to‑end Power BI analysis of hotel booking data. It covers data cleaning, 
creating a calendar table for time intelligence, and building an interactive Power BI dashboard to explore booking patterns,
revenue, and customer behavior.


⚡️ What I Worked On
Data Cleaning & Modeling: Prepared raw booking data for analysis and built relationships between tables.

Time Intelligence: Created a calendar table and used DAX measures for revenue and trend analyses across different time periods.

Visualization & Dashboard: Developed an interactive Power BI report, including metrics for revenue, lead times, cancellation patterns, and seasonal booking trends.

🎯 Goal
The goal of this project was to gain actionable insights into hotel bookings and revenues, allowing stakeholders to understand trends and make better decisions.
